                     <rubric>Text I:&#xD;
nomina sacra;&#xD;
names of the donors;&#xD;
three groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I-1;&#xD;
a quotation from Gospel of John (fol. 3vb);&#xD;
two lines on fol. 4ra;&#xD;
separate words and collocations (fols. 5r, 11ra, 20rb, 26ra, 26va, 26vb, 28rb, 45ra, etc.);&#xD;
incipits of miracles; &#xD;
elements of the punctuation signs (text dividers);&#xD;
elements of Ethiopic numerals&#xD;
Text II:&#xD;
nomina sacra;&#xD;
names of donors;&#xD;
three groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I-1;&#xD;
incipits of parts of Text II-1 and of miracles;&#xD;
incipit of Text III-3;&#xD;
elements of the punctuation signs (text dividers);&#xD;
elements of Ethiopic numerals</rubric>
