                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 48ra: Donation note. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 48ra: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮ ርጊስ፡ መነቦት፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ ለስርየተ፡ ኀጢአት፡ ወይባልሖ፡ እምኵኔኔ ፡[sic] ነፍስ፡ ዘእሳት። ኦአበውየ፡ ኢትርስኡኒ፡ በአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳቅሎስ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ለይኩን፡ ዘአጥረዮ፡ በንዋዩ፡ </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 81r: Unclear note with a list of names (?) </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 81r: በደጃዝማች፡ ሐጐስ፡ በቀኝዝማች፡ ወልደ፡ ስላሴ፡ &lt;...&gt; የኵሒላ፡ ነገር፡ ወዳዕ፡ ነገር፡ እንዳ፡ ገብርሔት የመጡ፡ ሁሉ ኃጎስና፡ ሸለቃ፡ ደስታ፡ አንድ፡ ናሽው። እማኝ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ህደሩ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ስንቄ። ዳኛ፡ ደስታ፡ የጐደታ፡ ፍስሀ፡ ውታፍ፡ ልጅ፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 81rb-va: Short hymn to Jesus Christ. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Pen trials: fol. 1v, 79va (?)&#xD;
- Scribbles: fols. 1r, 10r, 28r, 53r, 54r; recent scribbles: 2r, 48ra, 48vb, 49v, 50r, 64v, 65r, 76v, 77r, 77v, 78rb, 80ra, 80vb, 81ra, 81vb, 82r, 82v, 83r, 83v&#xD;
- A short note, barely legible: fol. 48vb&#xD;
Text I&#xD;
- Miracles are sometimes separated from each other by a line of alternating black and red dots (fol. 6va, 12v, 14ra)&#xD;
- Lacunae: fol. 26ra, 77vb.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words written interlineally, in the same hand: fols. 4ra, 6rb, 9rb, 10rb, 10va, 20rb, etc.&#xD;
- Omitted letters written in the margin: fols. 16va, 18ra&#xD;
- Correction written over erasure: fols. 18vb, 19vb, 29va, 30va, 31ra, 33ra&#xD;
Text II:&#xD;
- Lacuna: fol. 77vb&#xD;
- Omitted letters written interlineally, in the main hand: fol. 49ra&#xD;
- Omitted words written in the margin: fol. 78vb&#xD;
- Correction through blotting out: fol. 51va</item>
